snippet.title: Yokai Inn New Graphics Trailer
snippet.description:
Excited to reveal the new graphics makeover for the upcoming game Yokai Inn!

Run and manage an inn for spirits in this Japanese-inspired life sim game. Farm, cook, craft, customize, raise animals, and befriend folk both human and otherworldly alike!

Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/ShibaPixels
Join the Discord Server: discord.gg/yokai-inn
More: https://linktr.ee/ShibaPixels
